Class LandPredator

java.lang.Object
Animal
Predator
LandPredator
Direct Known Subclasses:
Cat, Fox
public class LandPredator extends Predator
The LandPredator class represents a specific type of predator that is a land predator. It extends the Predator class and includes additional information about the number of chick the LandPredator has killed.
